@node window_prefs_add_prefs "ignition - Window «Add Preferences»"
@toc windows
This window can only be accessed within the project local preferences. You can use it to add the listed preferences modules to your local preferences of a document.
Since you cannot apply all preferences modules in a local only context, you'll only see those modules listed which are possible to use in that way.
Contrary to the behaviour when you drag&drop other preferences to the project, every added preferences module will have the default settings.
@endnode


