@node troubleshooting "ignition - Troubleshooting"
 @{b}3.2. Troubleshooting@{ub}

 @{b}1. On save, the file type selection window does not appear, although the command explicetly asks for it@{ub}

The file type selection window is based on functionality found in the standard system ASL requester. Some ASL replacement requesters do not implement this functionality, and thus, are not 100% compatible.
To solve this, revert back to the original ASL requesters and you should be fine; its latest revisions are very fast and nice to use, too, anyway.

 @{b}2. I am using Picasso 96 and true color screens, but imported images are always dithered, and don't look good@{ub}


@endnode


